Raw Material = INTEG ( Ordering - Production Start, 1000 )
	~ Unit
	~ 
	|
Work In Process = INTEG ( Production Start - Production Finish, 500 )
	~ Unit
	~ 
	|
Finished Goods = INTEG ( Production Finish - Shipment, 200 )
	~ Unit
	~ 
	|
Ordering = ( Desired Raw Material - Raw Material ) / Adjustment Time
	~ Unit/Month
	~ 原材料订货率，一阶负反馈调整
	|
Desired Raw Material = Demand * Coverage Time
	~ Unit
	~ 期望原材料基于需求与覆盖时间
	|
Adjustment Time = 2
	~ Month
	~ 订货调整时间
	|
Coverage Time = 10
	~ Month
	~ 原材料覆盖时间
	|
Production Start = Raw Material * Production Rate
	~ Unit/Month
	~ 
	|
Production Rate = 0.5
	~ 1/Month
	~ 
	|
Production Finish = Work In Process * Completion Rate
	~ Unit/Month
	~ 
	|
Completion Rate = 0.4
	~ 1/Month
	~ 
	|
Shipment = MIN ( Finished Goods * Shipping Rate, Demand )
	~ Unit/Month
	~ 发货取产能与需求的较小值，需求驱动闭环
	|
Shipping Rate = 0.6
	~ 1/Month
	~ 
	|
Demand = 100 + STEP ( 50, 20 )
	~ Unit/Month
	~ 外部需求，第20月阶跃增加以测试响应
	|
INITIAL TIME = 0
	~ Month
	~ 
	|
FINAL TIME = 60
	~ Month
	~ 
	|
TIME STEP = 0.25
	~ Month
	~ 
	|
SAVEPER = TIME STEP
	~ Month
	~ 
	|
